snippet.title: ShowBiz Minute: CMT Awards, Heard, Brown
snippet.description:
McGraw, Underwood win big at CMT Awards; Amber Heard's ex-girlfriend defends actress in past arrest; Bobby Brown memoir alleges Houston smoked pot with daughter. (June 9)
